<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. von Aufseß, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Albrecht Fleischmann, Pfarrer zu St. Sebald in Nürnberg, wegen der Steuerforderungen der Amtleute des Adressaten an Gütern Nürnberger Bürger an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_415" id="206v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_415_r2l10"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bıſchof ʒu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_415_r2l11"><expan>Gneͣdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wir haben den <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Pfarrer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l12">ʒu ſand Sebold bey vns / gebetten / an eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu werben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l13">vnd ʒu reden von der <expan>anlagu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der ſteẅr / dıe etwıeuıl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>amptleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> beſchehen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l15">Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mit fleıſʒ / was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l16">der <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> ſachen . ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l17">an eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> werbe / Daʒ Jn eẅr gnade darinn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l18">verhörn . Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben . vnd <expan>gunſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l20"><expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> beweıſen wellet . als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l21">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . Dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r2l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_415" id="206v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, bischof zu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gneͣdig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir haben den
                                                  <expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, pfarrer zu sand
                                                Sebold bey uns, gebetten, an ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu werben
                                                und zu reden von der
                                                  <expan>anlagu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der stewr, die
                                                etwievil <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>amptlewt<ex>en</ex></expan> beschehen; und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mit
                                                fleisz, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der
                                                  <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> in den
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> sachen zu
                                                disem mal von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> werbe, daz
                                                in ewr gnade darinn
                                                  <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn, im des
                                                  <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und
                                                  <expan>gunstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> und den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten
                                                  <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen wellet.
                                                Als etc. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                                                wolgefallen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
